<item>
  <title>37signals Live is a show to watch</title>
  <description>
    &lt;h2&gt;First: 37signals rocks&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://live.37signals.com"&gt;&lt;img alt="37signals live logo" src="http://www.christophemaximin.com/files/37signals-live-logo.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This post will not be a surprise for anyone who is already following me on &lt;a href="http://twitter.com/christophe971" title="Follow me!"&gt;twitter&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a title="Add me!" href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=757483092"&gt;facebook&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#kolibria" title="I've been there all day and all night for almost three years, everyone is welcome!"&gt;irc&lt;/a&gt; :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am a HUGE fan of the guys at &lt;a href="http://37signals.com"&gt;37signals&lt;/a&gt; for a lot of reasons, here are some of them:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://loudthinking.com" title="David Heinemeier Hansson aka DHH"&gt;David&lt;/a&gt; is one of guys. He is &lt;a href="/files/dhh_fuck-you.jpg" title="When people are questioning the way he does things"&gt;cool&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="http://rubyonrails.org" title="I FUCKING LOVE RAILS - GOD DAMNIT"&gt;really cool&lt;/a&gt; and has &lt;a href="http://christophemaximin.com/2008/04/21/the-secret-to-making-money-online-by-my-hero-dhh" title="The secret to making money online"&gt;interesting things to say&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

    &lt;li&gt;They wrote the infamous &lt;a href="http://gettingreal.37signals.com/" title="A must read"&gt;Getting Real&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;Their blog, &lt;a href="http://www.37signals.com/svn/" title="aka SvN"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&lt;/strong&gt;ignal &lt;strong&gt;V&lt;/strong&gt;ersus &lt;strong&gt;N&lt;/strong&gt;oise&lt;/a&gt; is very interesting too&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Second: The show is great&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.christophemaximin.com/files/screenshot-37signals-Live.lq.jpg" title="Click to enlarge the screenshot of 37signals Live of 26/08/08"&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.christophemaximin.com/files/screenshot-37signals-Live.small.jpg" alt="screenshot of 37signals Live of 26/08/08" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So recently, David and Jason started a kind-of-weekly-but-not-really live show, strangely named "&lt;a href="http://live.37signals.com"&gt;37signals Live&lt;/a&gt;", where theyâ€™re answering to many questions mostly similar to "how do I get my web company on the tracks with not a lot of money". They have a "results oriented" and "real world" mindset which is very different than all the non-representative bullshit you can find of &lt;a href="http://techcrunch.com"&gt;Techcrunch&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The last show was about "Promotion", and if you missed it you can still find the videos &lt;a href="http://www.justin.tv/signals37/archive"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Last thing: there is no RSS for the show only yet, so if you want to know when the next one will be, just follow &lt;a href="http://www.37signals.com/svn/" title="aka SvN"&gt;their blog&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="http://twitter.com/37signals"&gt;twitter account&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
